<plot>Karen hates her life because of the repetitive tasks she had to accomplish as a mother and wife. Her perfect husband, Michael, and innocent son, Davy, force her to feel inadequate with her role. She sees herself as a failure with no satisfaction in life. Gradually, she draws herself away from the world and ultimately loses her identity.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?016332</url></doc>
